{"tid":1305432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 入嚟睇下","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T00:52:59.000Z","uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a893f34b8b226cbe29647d6c320a969ce7d731c1","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:09.000Z","msg":"噚日喺各戰線受傷同出嚟幫手嘅手足辛苦哂<br />\n噚日有手足為咗舉證就算畀人打都唔還手 <br />\n其實你係可以還手<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mcs.com.hk/%E4%BE%B5%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E7%BD%AA/?lang=zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcs.com.hk%2F%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F%3Flang%3Dzh-hant&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=2a3c95a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mcs.com.hk/%E4%BE%B5%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E7%BD%AA/?lang=zh-hant</a><br />\n法律上就算揮拳作勢都可以入普通襲擊<br />\n噚晚手足捱咗咁多嘢 相信用繩綁住佢 佢係無問題<br />\n因為只係阻止佢繼續襲擊人<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住 對方襲擊人 我哋只係保護自己同其他人<br />\n唔好再受傷啦大家"},{"pid":"ddcf8d38e7e232918a1e96b9e290e21599ea1aa5","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4773f515f9f7c948746cdb2d64eb7c2b83e0821b","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c64ac6b632b5e0060b438184fc8389e996ed71f","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a29d2116eb0440ce6961d44e76c47f4523120ab9","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e9f0b6987e4d36dbfa8f74c439a6a6cfa5b5379","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7330b4578cb9eae26f10ecf7d0adfea0c6ae435","tid":1305432,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:35:47.000